  "description": [
    "Friday 21 December 1962 Navy Nurses Graduated From NUOS Twentytwo Navy Nurse Corps Officers members of Class WN37 were graduated yesterday from Women Officers School here CAPT C S Stroud Jr Cruiser Destroyer Force Medical Officer and guest speaker presented di plomas to the graduates who rep resented 15 states 19 colleges universities or schools of nursing LT Joan F Swanson spoke as a representative of the graduating class Honor Student Mrs Michael Curran repre senting the Womens Division of the Newport County Chamber of Commerce presented an award to LTJG Nancy L Jobert in recog nition of her distinction in aca demic and military subjects which placed her first in her class Following the ceremony the Women iflicers School stall host ed a coffee for the graduates their parents and friends DesDevGru 2 Slates Annual Yule Partv The annual Christmas party for the children of Destroyer Devel opment Group Two will be held today at 1500 Bldg IS on Constel lation Landing The celebration includes refreshments a cartoon show and a gift for each child Because Santa will be unable to make a personal appearance at the party arrangements have been made for him to speak via closedcircuit TV"
